events in the NuDAF regime. In particular, detonations following\na white dwarf - neutron star merger could account for some subluminous Type Ia\nsupernovae, such as the class defined by SN 2002cx.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Sep 2012 20:00:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Dec 2012 21:18:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
