 with both the observationnal data of Gaulme\net al. (2011) and previous theoretical work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Sep 2012 20:55:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 23 Dec 2012 15:09:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
